{
  "name": "Medical Release Healing Elixir",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Medical.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use your medical kit to assist in creating a healing elixir which is contained in a simple vial that appears in your hand. The elixir retains its potency for the duration or until its consumed. As an action, a creature can drink the elixir or administer it to another creature. The drinker regains 3d4+3 hit points and immediately ends the Poisoned or removes 2 ranks of the Bleeding condition.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. When you cast this Jutsu at B-Rank, the drinker instead regains 3d8+6 Hit points and immediately ends the Poisoned, Dazed, Weakened or removes 4 ranks of the Bleeding condition. When cast at S-Rank, the drinker regains 3d12+9 and ends any single condition excluding Exhaustion, Prone, or Invisible.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
